data.description: Located in the HEART of Honolulu with close proximity to schools, shopping, hospitals, beaches & more. Park Tower sits on a bluff in the Punchbowl neighborhood with an open space feeling and offering Hawaiian sunset views every evening plus splendid views of the ocean and Honolulu skyline. This 3 bedroom 2 bath 2 parking unit comes with an additional outdoor lanai space of over 200 square feet. Bring all of your plants and your outdoor dining table! Unit needs some updating but comes freshly painted and with new, luxury carpet along with kitchen and bathroom fixtures that have been updated!  Monthly fees are presently  $1,093.25/month and include water, sewer & basic cable and WIFI. Come see today how easy city living can be! EZ to see.
